# 3. 切り拓け！

Akito: What's this doing here...?
Len: Akito, what's wrong?
Akito: Oh... I just found this.
Len: Huh? A flyer...?
Akito: Yeah, for an event I performed in way back when.
Rin: Cool!
Rin: Wait, but... I don't see “Vivid BAD SQUAD” written anywhere.
Akito: Well, it did happen a long time ago.
Akito: This was from back when I was in middle school. I entered by myself.
Len: Oh...! You mean the thing that Luka and the others mentioned the other day...?
Akito: Yeah... The event where I dragged Crawl Green's name through the mud...
Akito: Wait a second...
Akito: What if my painful emotions from back then are manifesting in SEKAI?
Len: Huh?
Akito: Before I started singing, I played soccer... But I hit a huge wall.
Akito: And now I've found a flyer of an event where I messed up.
Rin: Oh...
Akito: (Come to think of it...)
Akito: (I've messed up a lot.)
Akito: (The first time was with soccer when I got shown just how unprepared I really was.)
Akito: (Then, I saw RAD WEEKEND. I decided to start singing instead, but it didn't go as planned. One dumb argument led to me dragging that place's name through the mud.)
Akito: (After that, I met Toya and started practicing like there was no tomorrow. Even then, everyone kept making fun of us.)
Akito: (I managed to finally get this far... But I fell at so many hurdles.)
Len: In that respect, Akito, you're an amazing person.
Akito: Huh? Where's this coming from all of a sudden?
Len: Because you always keep trying no matter how hard things get...
Len: And now, your singing's so good it reignited all of Vivid Street!
Len: Which makes you...an amazing person!
Akito: Praise me all you want...
Rin: But I think Len's right!
Akito: Huh?
Rin: I mean, if I went through what you did, I'd probably have given up the first chance I could!
Len: Exactly! Not giving up is really hard!
Len: And you never did. You just kept blazing your own trail.
Len: Again, that's really amazing...and really cool!
Akito: (Cool, huh...?)
Akito: (I've never really thought of it that way.)
Akito: (I didn't think I had any other choice is all.)
Akito: (I couldn't quit. I couldn't show any weakness. Not after I decided I was gonna surpass that night. I'd never have forgiven myself if I did...)
Akito: (Which is why I can't see myself as being “cool”.)
Akito: (I mean, I've gotten better, but I'm still nowhere near my goal...)
Akito: (However...)
Akito: (I was able to sing with absolutely everything I had that time.)
Akito: (Which helped me figure out how to make everyone realize that we're serious...)
Akito: (I feel like I'm finally on the same level as them.)
Akito: (So...)
Akito: (Len might not be wrong.)
Len: What the...? Hey, Akito, check out the wall!
Akito: Hm? What happened?
Len: There's a big empty white box on it now! It wasn't there a second ago!
Rin: Yeah, he's right! Also...
Rin: Hmm... Is it just me, or does it look like a soccer goal?
Akito: A goal?
Akito: Yeah, it's about the right size...
Akito: (But why's a drawing of a goal appearing instead of an actual one?)
Akito: (It's like it wants me to kick the ball at that spot.)
Akito: ...!
Akito: Len, pass that ball to me...
Len: Huh? Why?
Akito: To give it the attention it deserves.
Akito: (I thought this flyer and ball appeared because of what I felt in the past.)
Akito: (But I might've been wrong.)
Akito: (I kept trying in the face of pain.)
Akito: (I kept pushing forward despite what I was feeling. I was determined to succeed.)
Akito: (And that determination is what's manifesting here.)
Akito: (Including that goal.)
Akito: (All the times I messed up, all that pain... It's telling me to take what I felt and use it to break down this wall.)
Akito: I know I'm gonna come across more walls in the future.
Akito: But they won't stop me. I'll always find a way through.
Akito: That's why I'm gonna keep doing everything I can to make that happen.
Len: Alright, Akito, it's your ball!
Rin: Whoa...! You did a tornado shot!!
Akito: No, that was just a regular mid-range shoot.
Len: But it was so fast! That was really cool, Akito!
Akito: Alright, quit exaggerating...
Akito: Hm...? Hey, did you guys hear that just now?
Akito: It sounded like something hard just cracked...
Rin: Look! There's a crack in the wall!!!
Akito: Huh...?!
Len: She's right! Akito, did you actually do a tornado shot?!
Akito: No, there's no way I kicked it that hard!
Rin: But it's definitely a crack...
Akito: What the heck's going on...?
